    <item>
      <title>摩科瑞与交易商一起进军日本现货电力市场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-04/mercuria-joins-trader-push-into-japan-s-spot-electricity-market</link>
      <description><![CDATA[摩科瑞能源集团有限公司 (Mercuria Energy Group Ltd.) 正准备开始在日本实物电力市场进行交易，这是最新一家寻求利用该行业不断上升的波动性的全球大宗商品公司。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-04/mercuria-joins-trader-push-into-japan-s-spot-electricity-market</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Apr 2024 12:27:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>贝莱德的博伊文：预计长期利率不会下降</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-04/blackrock-s-boivin-don-t-expect-long-term-rates-to-fall-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[贝莱德投资研究所(BlackRock Investment Institute)负责人让·博伊文(Jean Boivin)表示，“我们很可能会看到美联储开始降息，无论如何只会降息几次，然后同时看到稳定的长期利率稳定，甚至从这里走高。”]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-04/blackrock-s-boivin-don-t-expect-long-term-rates-to-fall-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Apr 2024 12:12:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>杰富瑞 (Jefferies) 与日本三井住友 (Sumitomo Mitsui) 将联盟扩大至加拿大</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-04/jefferies-japan-s-sumitomo-mitsui-expand-alliance-to-canada</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本最大的银行之一三井住友金融集团 (Sumitomo Mitsui Financial Group Inc.) 正在深化与杰富瑞金融集团 (Jefferies Financial Group Inc.) 的联盟，两家公司宣布计划在加拿大市场合作开展企业和投资银行业务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-04/jefferies-japan-s-sumitomo-mitsui-expand-alliance-to-canada</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Apr 2024 11:58:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲央行官员认为上个月降息的理由有所加强</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-04/ecb-officials-saw-case-for-rate-cut-strengthening-last-month</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行官员最新的政策会议记录显示，上个月，欧洲央行官员看到了足够令人信服的证据，得出降息时机即将到来的结论。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-04/ecb-officials-saw-case-for-rate-cut-strengthening-last-month</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Apr 2024 11:57:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度储备银行将外汇对冲规则的实施推迟至 5 月 3 日</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-04/india-rbi-pushes-back-fx-hedging-rule-implementation-to-may-3</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度央行将交易所交易货币衍生品规则的实施推迟了大约一个月，此前该措施引发了市场恐慌，因为交易员试图平仓未对冲头寸。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-04/india-rbi-pushes-back-fx-hedging-rule-implementation-to-may-3</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Apr 2024 11:54:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>选举焦虑使南非美元债券成为新兴市场表现最差的债券</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-04/election-anxiety-makes-south-africa-dollar-bonds-the-worst-in-em</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非美元债券的暴跌使其成为今年发展中市场中最大的落后者，反映出投资者担心下个月的选举中可能会出现一个对市场不友好的联合政府。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-04/election-anxiety-makes-south-africa-dollar-bonds-the-worst-in-em</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Apr 2024 11:49:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
